        <p class="hero-tagline">Systems That Play. Products That Last.</p>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          Game Designer &amp; Product Owner with 8+ years shaping MMORPG systems —
          from core mechanics and economy design to full product ownership.
          Currently leading the team behind <em>Silkroad Online Origin Mobile</em>.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View My Work</a>
