      <p class="section-intro reveal">
        Here's where design meets reality. These are projects where I was
        responsible for core game systems, product direction, or both —
        each shaped by data, refined by player feedback, and measured by real-world results.
      </p>

      <div class="projects-grid">

        <!-- PROJECT 1: Silkroad -->
        <article class="project-card project-card--featured reveal">
          <!--
            ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │  PLACEHOLDER: Silkroad Online Origin Mobile Banner      │
            │                                                         │
            │  Gợi ý ảnh:                                            │
