                <span>Best Gameplay</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chips">
              <span class="chip">Product Ownership</span>
              <span class="chip">MMORPG</span>
              <span class="chip">Mobile Adaptation</span>
              <span class="chip">Team Lead</span>
              <span class="chip">Combat System</span>
              <span class="chip">Full Reverse-Engineering</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Khi có case study page: đổi href sang /project/silkroad.html -->
            <a href="#" class="project-link">Read Case Study <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- PROJECT 2: Yulgang -->
        <article class="project-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
          <!--
            ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │  PLACEHOLDER: Yulgang Private Server Banner             │
            │                                                         │
            │  Gợi ý ảnh:                                            │
            │  • Screenshot gameplay đẹp nhất của server bạn         │
            │  • Key art / poster custom                              │
            │  • Tỉ lệ 16:9, min 1200×675px                          │
            │  • Khi có ảnh: xoá div.ph, thêm                        │
            │    <img src="images/yulgang-banner.jpg"                │
            │         class="project-banner" alt="Yulgang Server">   │
            └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
          -->
          <div class="ph project-banner">
            <div class="ph-icon">⚔️</div>
            <div class="ph-title">Project Banner — Yulgang</div>
            <div class="ph-hint">Screenshot gameplay hoặc Key Art<br>16:9, min 1200×675px</div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-body">
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="project-tag">Personal Project</span>
              <span class="project-tag">2017–2019</span>
              <span class="project-tag tag-role">Solo Founder & Designer</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="project-title">Yulgang Private Server<br>Hiệp Khách Giang Hồ</h3>
            <p class="project-impact">"Built a community of 780 concurrent players through thoughtful design."</p>
            <p class="project-desc">
              What started as nostalgia became a masterclass in game operations.
              I simultaneously held every role — player, QA, operator, community manager,
              and game designer — running a private server that reached 780 concurrent users
              and a 65% 7-day retention rate. More importantly, I successfully shifted the deeply
              traditional mindset of Yulgang players toward new systems and content.
            </p>
            <div class="project-stats">
              <div class="project-stat">
                <span class="stat-badge">👥</span>
                <span>780 Peak CCU</span>
              </div>
