              <span class="chip">Community Management</span>
              <span class="chip">Full Product Ownership</span>
            </div>
            <a href="https://minhbach.weebly.com/hi7879p-khaacutech-giang-h7891.html"
               target="_blank" class="project-link">View Project <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
