  <!-- ═══════ DESIGN THINKING ═══════ -->
  <section id="thinking">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-label"><span class="label-line"></span>Design Philosophy</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Beyond the<br><em>Feature List</em></h2>

      <div class="thinking-grid">
        <div class="thinking-text reveal">
          <p class="thinking-lead">
            A well-designed game isn't a collection of features — it's an ecosystem
            where every system reinforces the others.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I design a quest system, I'm thinking about how it feeds into the economy.
            When I balance combat, I'm considering how it affects player retention.
            When I plan monetization, I'm ensuring it enhances — not undermines — the core experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            This holistic approach comes from having operated games live. I've seen firsthand
            what happens when systems don't talk to each other: exploits, churn, broken economies.
            That's why I design with the full picture in mind.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="thinking-quote">
            "The best game systems are invisible — players feel the fun without seeing the architecture."
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="thinking-visual reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
          <!--
            ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │  PLACEHOLDER: Design Artifact                           │
            │                                                         │
            │  Gợi ý đặt 1 trong các loại ảnh sau:                   │
            │  • Game Loop Diagram bạn đã tạo                        │
            │  • Economy Flow Chart                                   │
            │  • System Interconnection Map                           │
            │  • Skill Progression Tree                               │
            │  • Combat Balance Spreadsheet (screenshot)              │
            │  • Wireframe / UX Flow từ bất kỳ project nào           │
            │  • Blur nhẹ nếu NDA, nhưng phải thấy được structure    │
            │                                                         │
            │  Khi có ảnh: xoá div.ph, thêm                          │
            │  <img src="images/design-artifact.jpg"                 │
            │       alt="Game system diagram">                       │
            └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
          -->
          <div class="ph thinking-artifact">
            <div class="ph-icon">📐</div>
            <div class="ph-title">Design Artifact</div>
            <div class="ph-hint">Game Loop Diagram / Economy Flow Chart /<br>System Map / Skill Tree / Balance Sheet<br>Blur nhẹ nếu NDA</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════ JOURNEY + TRUST SIGNALS (merged) ═══════ -->
  <section id="journey">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-label"><span class="label-line"></span>The Story</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">From QA to<br><em>Game of the Year</em></h2>
      <p class="section-intro reveal">
        A concise look at my work, growth, and achievements — one lesson at a time.
      </p>

      <div class="journey-timeline">

        <div class="j-item reveal">
          <div class="j-marker">
            <div class="j-dot"></div>
            <div class="j-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <div class="j-header">
              <span class="j-year">2017</span>
              <!--
                PLACEHOLDER: Logo Travian (40×40px PNG nền trong suốt)
                <img src="images/logo-travian.png" class="j-logo" alt="Travian">
              -->
              <div class="ph j-logo-ph"></div>
              <span class="j-company">Collaboration · Travian</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="j-title">The Start — How Players Play the Game</h3>
            <p class="j-desc">
              Monitored player activity logs to detect abnormal accounts and provided customer support.
              Beyond the org's framework, independently researched player behavior — understanding how
              players exploit loopholes and the in-game legal system.
            </p>
            <div class="j-lesson">
              <span class="j-lesson-label">Key Insight:</span>
              Understanding player behavior at the ground level became the foundation of every design decision I'd make later.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="j-item reveal">
          <div class="j-marker">
            <div class="j-dot"></div>
            <div class="j-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <div class="j-header">
              <span class="j-year">2018–2019</span>
              <!--
                PLACEHOLDER: Logo Yulgang hoặc server icon (40×40px)
                <img src="images/logo-yulgang.png" class="j-logo" alt="Yulgang">
              -->
              <div class="ph j-logo-ph"></div>
              <span class="j-company">Game Op & Design · Yulgang Private</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="j-title">The Build-Up — How a Product Runs</h3>
            <p class="j-desc">
              Led product planning and managed all in-game &amp; out-of-game operations.
              Designed and balanced systems, content, and features as a one-person team.
              Developed new features later adopted by other private servers.
            </p>
            <div class="j-achievements">
              <span class="j-badge">780 CCU</span>
              <span class="j-badge">RR7 65%</span>
              <span class="j-badge accent">Shifted player mindset</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="j-item reveal">
          <div class="j-marker">
            <div class="j-dot"></div>
            <div class="j-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <div class="j-header">
              <span class="j-year">2020</span>
              <!--
                PLACEHOLDER: Logo SOHAGAMES (40×40px)
                <img src="images/logo-sohagames.png" class="j-logo" alt="SOHAGAMES">
              -->
              <div class="ph j-logo-ph"></div>
              <span class="j-company">Game Operation · SOHAGAMES</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="j-title">The Foundation — How to Work as an Organization</h3>
            <p class="j-desc">
              Oversaw live operations, proposed data-driven product improvements, conducted market
              &amp; community research. Transformed intuition into a data-driven mindset.
            </p>
            <div class="j-achievements">
              <span class="j-badge accent">110%+ KPI × 10 months</span>
              <span class="j-badge">Best Project 2020</span>
              <span class="j-badge">Fastest Break-Even 2020</span>
              <span class="j-badge gold">★ Outstanding Employee 2020</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="j-item reveal">
          <div class="j-marker">
            <div class="j-dot"></div>
            <div class="j-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <div class="j-header">
              <span class="j-year">2021–2022</span>
              <!--
                PLACEHOLDER: Logo ATEAM hoặc GihOt (40×40px)
                <img src="images/logo-ateam.png" class="j-logo" alt="ATEAM">
              -->
              <div class="ph j-logo-ph"></div>
              <span class="j-company">Live-ops Design · ATEAM &amp; GihOt Studio</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="j-title">The Acceleration — Beyond Operation</h3>
            <p class="j-desc">
              <strong>ATEAM:</strong> Product ops evolving into Live Ops Designer.
              Discovered a long-standing balance bug via gacha data analysis.<br>
              <strong>GihOt:</strong> Full ownership of a hardcore MMORPG core systems in 30 days.
              Sole fresher given full authority to overhaul a full MMORPG.
            </p>
            <div class="j-achievements">
              <span class="j-badge gold">★ Promising Employee 2022</span>
            </div>
