        <div class="j-item j-item--current reveal">
          <div class="j-marker">
            <div class="j-dot j-dot--active"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <div class="j-header">
              <span class="j-year">2025</span>
              <!--
                PLACEHOLDER: Logo Silkroad hoặc công ty hiện tại (40×40px)
                <img src="images/logo-silkroad.png" class="j-logo" alt="Silkroad">
              -->
              <div class="ph j-logo-ph"></div>
              <span class="j-company">Game Design Team Lead</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="j-title">The Reward — Silkroad Online Origin Mobile</h3>
            <p class="j-desc">
              Planned entire product vision for "Recreating the Silk Road World."
              Designed all core systems: world, characters, stats, skills, equipment.
              Led design team, rebalanced the full product for mobile.
              Fully reverse-engineered PC version. The only individual to reconstruct
              the original Silkroad combat formula.
            </p>
            <div class="j-achievements">
              <span class="j-badge gold">🏆 Best Gameplay</span>
              <span class="j-badge gold">🏆 Best Graphics</span>
              <span class="j-badge gold">🏆 Game of the Year</span>
